        <div><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-------------------------------------=
--------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+ Commands output at when =
the Spindle first turns on.</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+------------=
---------------------------------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>b=
egin SPINDLE_ON</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>"Commands"</code></p><p c=
lass=3D"mt-3">The Spindle On section was added to allow for Spindle and Las=
er operations in the same Post Processor instead of having the Spindle on c=
ommand as part of the header. </p><p class=3D"mt-3">Typically this will jus=
t have the Spindle on command (M03 for example) but can also include a Spin=
dle speed command [S] </p></div>
