2.0/VCarvePro/shared/icons/link.svg">
            </a>
         =20
          TOOLCHANGE
        </h3>
        <div><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-------------------------------------=
--------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+ Commands output at toolc=
hange</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+----------------------------------=
-----------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>begin TOOLCHANGE</code>=
</p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>"Commands"</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3">Commands=
 that are output when a change of tool is required. Variables and commands =
that might be used include:</p><ul><li>Previous Tool Number =3D [TP]</li><l=
i>Tool Number =3D [T]</li><li>Tool name =3D [TOOLNAME]</li><li>Toolpath Nam=
e =3D [TOOLPATH_NAME]</li><li>Toolpath Pathname =3D [PATHNAME]</li><li>Tool=
path File Name =3D [TP_FILENAME]</li><li>Toolpath File Directory =3D [TP_DI=
R]</li><li>Toolpath Extension =3D [TP_EXT]</li><li>Spindle Speed =3D [S] R.=
P.M.</li><li>M3 M Code often used to turn spindle on (Clockwise rotation).<=
/li><li>M5 M Code often used to turn spindle off.</li></ul></div>
