       =20
          <a class=3D"inline-block" href=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs/V=
12.0/VCarvePro/ENU/Help/form/post-processor-editing/#2a1314f8022c">
            <img loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs/V12.=
0/VCarvePro/shared/icons/link.svg">
          </a>
       =20
        Jet Support Sections
      </h2>
      <p class=3D"mt-3">These sections are for supporting jet-based cutting=
 tools such as lasers, plasmas and waterjets.</p>
     =20
        <h3 id=3D"724b33f8380c" class=3D"text-xl font-semibold p-2 mb-2 mt-=
6 font-bold font-raleway overflow-hidden">
         =20
            <a class=3D"inline-block" href=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs=
/V12.0/VCarvePro/ENU/Help/form/post-processor-editing/#724b33f8380c">
              <img loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs/V1=
2.0/VCarvePro/shared/icons/link.svg">
            </a>
         =20
          JET_TOOL_POWER
        </h3>
        <div><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-------------------------------------=
--------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+ Commands output when the=
 cutter's power is set</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-----------------=
----------------------------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>begin =
JET_TOOL_POWER</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>"Commands"</code></p><p cl=
ass=3D"mt-3"><em>For an example of a JET_TOOL_POWER section, see the file: =
Grbl.pp</em></p><p class=3D"mt-3">Commands that are output when the power s=
etting associated with a laser 'tool' is issued.</p></div>
     =20
        <h3 id=3D"f043c0237e9a" class=3D"text-xl font-semibold p-2 mb-2 mt-=
6 font-bold font-raleway overflow-hidden">
         =20
            <a class=3D"inline-block" href=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs=
/V12.0/VCarvePro/ENU/Help/form/post-processor-editing/#f043c0237e9a">
              <img loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs/V1=
2.0/VCarvePro/shared/icons/link.svg">
            </a>
         =20
          JET_TOOL_ON
        </h3>
        <div><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-------------------------------------=
--------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+ Commands output when the=
 cutter's power is turned ON</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-----------=
----------------------------------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>=
begin JET_TOOL_ON</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>"Commands"</code></p><p=
 class=3D"mt-3"><em>For an example of a JET_TOOL_ON section, see the file: =
Grbl.pp</em></p><p class=3D"mt-3">Commands that are output when the jet too=
l is powered on. This is broadly equivalent to SPINDLE_ON, but is typically=
 issued a the end of a plunge move when the jet cutter is already at the in=
tended cutting height, instead of before the plunge move as required by a s=
pindle based cutter.</p></div>
     =20
        <h3 id=3D"8b266b773481" class=3D"text-xl font-semibold p-2 mb-2 mt-=
6 font-bold font-raleway overflow-hidden">
         =20
            <a class=3D"inline-block" href=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs=
/V12.0/VCarvePro/ENU/Help/form/post-processor-editing/#8b266b773481">
              <img loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"https://docs.vectric.com/docs/V1=
2.0/VCarvePro/shared/icons/link.svg">
            </a>
         =20
          JET_TOOL_OFF
        </h3>
        <div><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+-------------------------------------=
--------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+ Commands output when the=
 cutter's power is turned OFF</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>+----------=
-----------------------------------------</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code=
>begin JET_TOOL_OFF</code></p><p class=3D"mt-3"><code>"Commands"</code></p>=
<p class=3D"mt-3"><em>For an example of a JET_TOOL_OFF section, see the fil=
e: Grbl.pp</em></p><p class=3D"mt-3">Commands that are output when the jet =
tool is powered off.</p></div>
     =20
    </div>
